snippet.title: Tenchi Muyou! Mimiri Onsen -  Yukemuri no Tabi - Pt 1 (Sega Saturn)
snippet.description:
To my knowledge there is no English translation available for this release. I used google translate to try to understand the menu choices and incidental text but as for the dialogue, I have no idea what is going on. LOL

Captured via Mednafen and OBS.
